full_title: PAPERWORK by ¥$, Kanye West & Ty Dolla $ign (Ft. Quavo)
title: PAPERWORK

description.plain:
Track 8 from Kanye West and Ty Dolla $ign’s Vultures 1. After weeks of speculation, insiders confirmed that that are two versions of the song: one featuring Quavo and one featuring Lil Wayne.

A lyric of the song was made out alongside a snippet of the song leaked on January 21, 2024, with the song seeing an official performance at United Centre Vultures Listening Party on February 8th of that year.

The song samples MONTAGEM FAZ MACETE 3.0 by DJ Vitinho Beat and DJ Roca, and was officially released alongside the album on February 10th, 2024.

Track 8 from Kanye West and Ty Dolla $ign’s Vultures 1. After weeks of speculation, insiders confirmed that that are two versions of the song: one featuring Quavo and one featuring Lil Wayne.

A lyric of the song was made out alongside a snippet of the song leaked on January 21, 2024, with the song seeing an official performance at United Centre Vultures Listening Party on February 8th of that year.

The song samples MONTAGEM FAZ MACETE 3.0 by DJ Vitinho Beat and DJ Roca, and was officially released alongside the album on February 10th, 2024.
